Here is the translation:

The servant of God is Ram's servant, why say "Jeev" and know wisdom; 
After said thus is Dharma, listen to devotion, I say the inner soul.

Here is the translation:

This statue looks beautiful many times, how does it look this way; 
Garment of Hem's color is in hand, turban wound on head tight.

Here is the translation:

Krishna says: Dhanakar Rathapati are blessed, they take blissful forms; 
You are Sri Krishna's Brahman completion, you have all reasons as your reason.

Here is the translation:

Ajugarthi chodaavya Nand re, tame maaryo Shankachood mand re;
Vrusabh ne vyomasur dweshire re, tame maaryo bale Khal keesi re.
